title: Gamecube NinTrendo 5/1: Ashlee Simpson, Erykah Badu v Jill Scott, Valorant, Tony Allen
itunes:title: Gamecube NinTrendo 5/1: Ashlee Simpson, Erykah Badu v Jill Scott, Valorant, Tony Allen
description:
On this edition of Gamecube NinTrendo Miles and DJ Danl discuss Ashlee Simpson expecting her first child, Erykah Badu and Jill Scott are facing off in the next VERZUZ Battle on IG Live, Valorant have activated their Ranked playlists, and legendary Afrobeat drummer Tony Allen has passed away at 79.
